      • getNewLanguageManager

        public LanguageManager getNewLanguageManager()
        Gets a newly created private instance of a language manager, this instance will **NOT** be stored within UneiLang.

        The preset folder will be set to the default one, you may want to change it using LanguageManager.setPresetFolder(File).

        Returns:
        Returns a private instance of a language manager.

      • getNewPlayerManager

        public PlayerLanguageManager getNewPlayerManager()
        Gets a newly created private instance of a player manager, this instance will **NOT** be stored within UneiLang.

        Auto-saving will be enabled by default, you can change it using PlayerLanguageManager.setAutoSaving(boolean).

        Returns:
        Returns a private instance of a player manager.
